  h3 Architecture
  p Once I had an idea of our design direction, I created documents for sitemap, color palette, and font choices. 
  .case-study-illustration
    img(src="/assets/img/case-studies/sitemap.png", alt="Sorba Atlanta site map.")
  .case-study-illustration
    img(src="/assets/img/case-studies/colors.png", alt="Sorba Atlanta colors.")
  h3 Wireframes
  p I provided <strong>detailed wireframes</strong> for all pages of the site. I looked for <strong>approval and improvement</strong> with each step forward.
  .case-study-illustration
    img(src="/assets/img/case-studies/home-wireframe.png", alt="Sorba Atlanta wireframe.")
  h3 Build
  p Once I had approval on our wireframes, I gave flesh to their bones and wireframes became comps. I used the wonderful <a href="https://www.invisionapp.com/">Invision app</a> to make these comps functional, allowing Brett to get a feel for the flow of the site.
  .case-study-illustration
    img(src="/assets/img/case-studies/home-comp.png", alt="Sorba Atlanta comp.")
  p Turning pretty pictures into a working website is no small task. I sat down with my favorite text editor and built a <strong>custom WordPress theme</strong> from scratch, making sure that every pixel was in its place and that my code was <strong>clean and semantic</strong>. The final site can be found <a href="http://sorba.resolutionathens.com/">here</a>.
  .case-study-illustration
    img(src="/assets/img/case-studies/sorba-after.jpg", alt="Sorba Atlanta after the redesign.")
  h3 Evolve
  p We are working with Brett and the board at Sorba Atlanta to provide WordPress training, including the use of the <a href="https://givewp.com/">Give donation plugin</a>. We are also providing them with a content calendar for regular updates, creating campaigns for email and social media, and setting up Google Analytics to monitor the success of our continuing efforts.
  p I  hope that this case study was informative if not entertaining. If you entrust your project to us, we will sweat every detail and do everything we can to earn it.
